@tacigar curious what you use to make animated gif for before and after..

I think there are some problems in `component_ui/trace.js`
For example, in https://github.com/openzipkin/zipkin/blob/510434c88ecd1750d5a36164d46c06e3e2958b07/zipkin-ui/js/component_ui/trace.js#L56-L59 I think the code should be like the following.

```
    $.each(children[$selected.id], (j, cId) => {
      family.add(cId);
      $selected.openChildren -= 1;
      spans[cId].openParents -= 1;
      spans[cId].inFilters -= 1;
    });
```
I think the essential problems are in these processes.
